{"tid":1240922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"網上 \"Tap n Go\" App 訂閱蘋果動新聞教學 (夠11歲就用得)","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:46:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24db961a5433c61721395c7dcfeeb77a51d151a6","tid":1240922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"網上 &quot;Tap n Go&quot; App 訂閱蘋果動新聞教學 (夠11歲就用得)<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n啱啱用 &quot;Tap n Go&quot; App 成功訂閱咗 蘋果動新聞   (夠11歲就用得)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oq1Xhg8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOq1Xhg8.png&h=b987fceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n原來唔太難<br />\n<br />\n首先 download and install 咗 Tap n Go App<br />\n<br />\n呢度<br />\n <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hktpayment.tapngo&amp;hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.hktpayment.tapngo%26hl%3Den&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=e930023a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hktpayment.tapngo&amp;hl=en</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blClJZ2sHQSnK95cDqXVYY3gIrcW4XzZzWa_CdhoMV1ghZVoUXoie8OVXXH7gb2VGcw=s180-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FblClJZ2sHQSnK95cDqXVYY3gIrcW4XzZzWa_CdhoMV1ghZVoUXoie8OVXXH7gb2VGcw%3Ds180-rw&h=107e93a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住呢度做嚟啟動張 網上 mastercard 預付 card<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tapngo.com.hk/chi/apply.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tapngo.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fapply.html&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=58a65037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tapngo.com.hk/chi/apply.html</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住去 7-11 或 Circle K 增值<br />\n<br />\n增值完就可以去 蘋果訂閱 網上webpage 用呢張網上預付 mastercard 嚟訂閱<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩問題可以係度問,  識既我會盡答, 因為啱啱先開完張卡, 增值, 訂閱埋.<br />\n(原來喺 youtube 既 Super Chat 都用到, 啱啱試埋, work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n其他識答既巴絲都可以答既,  互相幫忙, 唔該晒.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"19d1dd23428f0ce3c84d5fc7bc55d6425c67b3db","tid":1240922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9b33a25ae4c31464d457dee311de698db9112c4","tid":1240922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:08:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"517b841884b49327cf94bd705cbd82fdbbfa10fe","tid":1240922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"7月4日下午起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/images/welovehk_title3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fimages%2Fwelovehk_title3.png&h=77a81a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMxv7br.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMxv7br.jpg&h=347a307e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}